sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para: The external interfaces are represented by the generated RTE based on the ZKMEBINT_SstSr.xml sst file. ZKMEBINT_SstSr.xml is exported from SST_ZKMEBINT.xlsx with the mapping set in the ZKMEBINT_SstSr.xsd file.

sect1.title: External Dependencies
sect1.para: The external dependencies of the component are the library functions: init_zkmebint and cyclic_zkmebintpre.
